title.rendered: Natan Couture FW23 collection during Paris Couture Week

content.rendered:
NATAN. Couture AH23 collection, during Paris Couture Week.

NATAN Couture AH23 collection, which was presented during Paris Couture Week to celebrate the 40th anniversary of the Maison.

Runway looks


Photo: Press NATAN.

More on: @natancouture

Thanks: @carolinecharlescommunication


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
